Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:01.93,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多部正在招新~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩竞技歌留多吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 我们是歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来加入歌留多部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加入我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是歌留多部~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才那位同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很适合穿袴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 一起来玩歌留多好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿上袴之类的一定很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年时穿就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你对歌留多有兴趣吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实歌留多是一门激烈的运动…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试就知道…了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不再多找一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能被承认为正式的部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然那么难提起他们的兴趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很快就能找到合适的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题 是关于这个原子所构成的分子的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例题中 电子 质子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及中子的数量相等的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周继续讲解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好预习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 女帝刚才瞪着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡得可死了 怎么啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就在做歌留多部的招新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连早饭也没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千和驹野同学 都很辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始先把100张比赛用牌面朝下洗匀…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后双方各拿25张 在己方的阵地上摆好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的50张称为「空牌」 将不会使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵地宽87厘米 纵向分为三段…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书桌小子你很积极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得赶紧追上大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那从今天开始好好练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭得好好地吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你听见了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个教室都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可乐饼面包已经卖完了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}可乐饼是将面粉和其他配料\N混在一起炸出来的一种食品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.08,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}请给我一盒咖啡牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:23.66,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:24.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:25.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒面面包已经卖完了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}大婶 那我要两个红豆包吧 这是钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:32.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现肉包小子啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等输给我了再去买肉包子吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.05,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fade(245,0,255,0,900,4040,5050)\pos(474,206)}飞练余枯影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:05.05,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fade(245,0,255,0,900,4040,5050)\pos(394,455)}久绝钟磬音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要尽快抢到读到的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将己方阵地的牌数变成零的一方获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在己阵中的情况我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到对方阵中的牌的时候 又该怎么做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个情况下 就可以从己阵中选一张牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把它…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叫做「送牌」…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送牌是很重要的 能极大地左右比赛的走向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个可以送牌的场合 是在「手误」的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读的是空牌却碰到了场上的牌 就是手误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应牌是在己阵中 却碰到敌阵中的牌 也是手误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应牌在敌阵中却碰到了己阵中的牌 也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算碰到了错误的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当其与对应牌在同一阵地中时 则不构成手误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包…我发现肉包了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…肉包?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙原来跟我们在同一个高中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 他那身打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网球部?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么非得躲起来啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也说不清为啥啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才恳求他加入歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有经验的人就给我加入歌留多部啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有经验的人就给我加入歌留多部吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.02,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这冷不丁地干什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别胡说! 千早只是迟到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一也在歌留多部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望肉包小子你无论如何都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫「西田」!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多部的事 我刚才不是已经拒绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田…你不玩歌留多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明很强的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩歌留多也不会有什么好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又土气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我初中的时候就一直在打网球了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算高中也继续打下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 要玩歌留多的话可以去歌留多会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要专门在社团活动的时候玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果肉包小子加入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的歌留多部一定会变得很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想肉包同学也肯定会变强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那个兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该去参加社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的名字不是肉包 是西田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 稍等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 西田! 就是这个状态!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山川 你发球时不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子的运动神经很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候相比的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.62,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたのはら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「扬帆济沧海…」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.41,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…こ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…极」!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:00.95,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたのはら…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「扬帆济沧海…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.62,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…や!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…岛」!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.05,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あさぼらけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寒夜连清晓…」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.71,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…う!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…雾」!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六字决定牌的判断点?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一球!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.39,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よのなかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「世间千般愁」!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 换人!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去捡球吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.53,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やまのおくにも　しかぞなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「循山觅幽隐 鹿鸣复添伤」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子 你果然应该玩歌留多的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是没完没了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你玩网球是为了代替歌留多对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话网球很可怜的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟你没关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再来烦我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在活动室等你!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田 脚步没跟上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好盯着球!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了太慢了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 西田?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…我想早退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下一个 二年级的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在含有读到的牌的阵地中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算碰到的不是对应牌 也不会构成「手误」 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上句的朗读过程中有相同部分的这两张牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「粗缆直艚头」和「世间千般愁」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.86,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,658)}よのなかは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.86,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,658)}よのなかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们叫做「友牌」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两张牌 在听到第五个字之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能确定哪张是对应牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果像这样子 在同一个阵地中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要听到「よの」这两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能一口气把它们都扫出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手也能很容易抢到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当友牌都在己阵的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把其中一张送给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽早将它们分到不同阵中 也是一种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打断一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了是「西田」!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要会错意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来入部的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想着来看看你们都在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不到小学生的水平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位才刚刚入门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子加入的话 水平会提升的!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个人水平高也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那么厉害的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩歌留多是需要天赋的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我们这样的不管再怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是赢不了绵谷新的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 你们加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会在网球上下功夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你和西田比一场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是浪费时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早一直没有放弃过歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不断努力的人会变得多强…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就亲眼看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你知道必败所以不肯上?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 小学的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对刚入门的千早也只是勉勉强强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就更没底了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子 来玩歌留多吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…给我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛要是我赢的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别再来缠着我!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要请我吃一个月的肉包!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗记时间结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:56.17,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「花映难波津 隆冬且暂隐」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:56.17,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:01.38,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:01.38,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初春又将至 再绽此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:08.35,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是序歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朗读完这首歌之后 比赛就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.06,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つきみれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「寒夜望冷月…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.35,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うかりける…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「初濑谒观音…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.31,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたのはら　やそしまかけて…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「扬帆济沧海 岛夷万千…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从千早那连着抢走了三张…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为我技术生疏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果身体还是很轻巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来打网球也有点帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可没闲工夫在那笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:50.30,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ひとにはつげよ　あまのつりぶね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:50.30,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「钓舟烦相告 孤影别萍踪」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我获胜的时候 都能得到表扬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:58.23,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,めぐりあひて　みしやそれとも　わかぬまに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「久别逢交旧 欲诉万千言」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 优征!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就能升上A级了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前 要获得全国大会的冠军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始玩歌留多 纯粹因为觉得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时 却变得以获胜为唯一目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后遇到了那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我深深体会到了什么叫天赋的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才逃避了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避了歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早又抢到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田同学还剩17张 绫濑则是15张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉…我竟然落后了两张…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:04.29,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ひるはきえつつ　ものをこそおもへ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:04.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「我心亦如是 恋灼此身摧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要再集中一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要扭转比赛形势!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.63,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しのぶれど…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「闺情芳心宿…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻敌阵 扭转了形势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会送出哪张牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很在意友牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(600,691)}·
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心思完全被猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早原来打算把「得君」和「苦恋」这两张友牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,658)}いまこ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.76,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,658)}いまは
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用渡手的方式来抢掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:03.48,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ものやおもふと　ひとのとふまで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:03.48,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「他人戏相问 方知恋已深」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.52,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うらみわび…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恨更泪成雨…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.53,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しらつゆに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「秋色润原野…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田把形势逆转 领先一张牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后半一向很强的千早…居然被压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉 真怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子你并没有讨厌歌留多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个先不说 你可别忘了承诺啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我绝对不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:50.28,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つらぬきとめぬ　たまぞちりける
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「风拂真珠散 流光落玉盘」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.28,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「静…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.03,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…ととぎす
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…夜待子规」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.58,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ちぎり…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「共结…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.20,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…きな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…山盟誓」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:04.62,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「晴…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.21,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…さかたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…春淡日暖」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「晴春」应该是二字决定牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.84,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,658)}ひさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才是碰运气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概有那么一些牌 千早能听到接下来的一个音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她的感觉特别好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的一个音?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,己阵还剩5张牌 敌阵剩4张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前半分开的两张「いま」的友牌也该念到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌阵的「いま」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,己阵的「いま」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下比的就是气势了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念己阵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念己阵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快念己阵的吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.75,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまはただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.75,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「苦恋不得允…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明猜到了 却抢不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到实力差距被她拉开这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这个单纯喜欢歌留多而已的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(522,691)}·
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(562,691)}·
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前玩歌留多的时候 也像这家伙一样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着这样坚定的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您辛苦了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很精彩的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有参考价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很强啊 肉包小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 要不要跟我们一起组建歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我一个人真的不是千早的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有像你这么强的对手的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 肉包小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再勉强你加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 跟我比赛歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是早退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会在这种地方偷懒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田同学 给我好好解释一下这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要退出网球部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想玩歌留多!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田同学 你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这些家伙说…没有我的话这个部就无法成立了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是对歌留多…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网球是无法代替歌留多的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么尽快上交退部申请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有这最后一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西田 谢谢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作为我同意入部的交换 真岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让这家伙别再叫我「肉包小子」了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 为什么啊 肉包小子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说别再叫我「肉包」了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦肉包小子 再比一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊! 我要报仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…都说别再叫我「肉包」了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再孤独了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
